33
00:03:01,450 --> 00:03:01,840
Okay.

34
00:03:02,150 --> 00:03:02,810
That's all.

35
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:03,290
Okay.

36
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:07,710
The acupuncture needles will
stay in place for half an hour.

37
00:03:07,710 --> 00:03:09,870
If you feel uncomfortable at any point,
call me immediately.

38
00:03:09,870 --> 00:03:11,430
I still have patients next door.

39
00:03:11,430 --> 00:03:12,030
Thank you.

40
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:17,190
Does it hurt?

41
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:18,770
I'm fine.

42
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,410
Lie down for a while.

43
00:03:22,630 --> 00:03:23,690
I'm full of energy.

44
00:03:42,500 --> 00:03:43,120
Mingxi,

45
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,610
thank goodness everything has been resolved,

46
00:03:44,610 --> 00:03:45,910
and you can still take the midterm exams.

47
00:03:45,910 --> 00:03:46,710
That's great.

48
00:03:47,030 --> 00:03:49,430
