49
00:03:49,890 --> 00:03:51,650
How has your studying at home been going?

50
00:03:51,650 --> 00:03:52,460
I think

51
00:03:52,490 --> 00:03:54,190
I have a real shot at that scholarship this time.

52
00:03:54,190 --> 00:03:54,710
Really?

53
00:04:02,030 --> 00:04:02,830
What's wrong?

54
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:05,490
Who is it?

55
00:04:05,790 --> 00:04:06,600
Chen Sujie.

56
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,400
Him again?

57
00:04:09,860 --> 00:04:12,660
I've been going with him to his treatments lately.

58
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:13,710
Treatments?

59
00:04:14,050 --> 00:04:15,270
Chen Sujie is sick?

60
00:04:15,530 --> 00:04:17,730
Didn't he just have a game a few days ago?

61
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:19,480
Mingxi...

62
00:04:20,190 --> 00:04:21,190
actually,

63
00:04:21,220 --> 00:04:22,280
there's something

64
00:04:22,390 --> 00:04:23,950
I've been keeping from you.

65
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:25,360
If I tell you,

66
00:04:25,390 --> 00:04:26,850
