67
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:31,160
I promised to keep it for him.

68
00:04:31,430 --> 00:04:32,430
The condition was

69
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:34,800
that I accompany him to physiotherapy.

70
00:04:35,750 --> 00:04:36,240
Nian,

71
00:04:36,450 --> 00:04:38,250
