72
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:40,970
Alright,

73
00:04:41,070 --> 00:04:42,270
that's just like you.

74
00:04:43,630 --> 00:04:44,960
This time is different.

75
00:04:47,080 --> 00:04:48,540
I heard my heart pounding.

76
00:04:51,930 --> 00:04:52,930
Your heart.

77
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:56,520
By the way,

78
00:04:56,640 --> 00:04:58,370
what about you and Jiang Bohan?

79
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:16,160
Corn,

80
00:05:16,180 --> 00:05:16,910
you're back?

81
00:05:25,610 --> 00:05:26,740
Who the hell are you?

82
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:28,560
I'm...

83
00:05:29,270 --> 00:05:29,750
I'm...

84
00:05:30,250 --> 00:05:31,050
Wang Chunian.

85
00:05:33,630 --> 00:05:35,290
I wasn't asking for your name,

86
00:05:35,510 --> 00:05:37,510
