87
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:41,720
What's wrong?

88
00:05:44,070 --> 00:05:46,070
This is my classmate, Wang Chunian.

89
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:48,610
This is my former neighbor's son,

90
00:05:48,870 --> 00:05:49,600
You Jingchu.

91
00:05:50,159 --> 00:05:52,090
Why did your former neighbor's son

92
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,520
take a bath at your place?

93
00:05:54,210 --> 00:05:55,260
It's a long story.

94
00:05:55,440 --> 00:05:55,790
Come with me,

95
00:05:55,790 --> 00:05:57,590
I'll explain everything to you.

96
00:06:05,290 --> 00:06:07,320
The midterm exam begins now.

97
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:10,000
Time limit: 1 hour and 30 minutes.

98
00:06:12,590 --> 00:06:16,870
[Name: Yu Mingxi]

99
00:07:16,730 --> 00:07:17,510
Exams are over!

100
00:07:17,510 --> 00:07:18,310
Finally free!

101
00:07:18,750 --> 00:07:20,040
Finally finished.

102
00:07:21,070 --> 00:07:21,870
How did you do?

103
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:23,640
I think I did pretty well!

104
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:26,360
So does that mean you have a chance of
getting the scholarship?

105
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,160
Absolutely!

106
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:28,940
Here I come, scholarship!

107
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:30,090
I'll have money!

108
00:07:30,190 --> 00:07:32,320
I can pay my rent and buy running shoes!

109
00:07:46,190 --> 00:07:46,720
Nian!

110
00:07:47,630 --> 00:07:48,490
My name is on it!

111
00:07:49,370 --> 00:07:49,680
One,

112
00:07:49,700 --> 00:07:49,870
two,

113
00:07:49,870 --> 00:07:50,070
three,

114
00:07:50,070 --> 00:07:50,409
four,

115
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:51,000
five,

116
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:51,240
six,

117
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:51,640
seven.

118
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:52,390
You got seven A's,

119
00:07:52,390 --> 00:07:52,950
Mingxi!

120
00:07:53,190 --> 00:07:53,800
Seven A's.

121
00:07:53,820 --> 00:07:54,510
Seven A's.

122
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:56,720
But

123
00:07:56,870 --> 00:07:59,310
even though I made it into the top 50 this time,

124
00:07:59,310 --> 00:08:01,570
there are only three scholarship spots.

125
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:07,560
Excuse me,

126
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:09,020
excuse me, make way, please.

127
00:08:09,020 --> 00:08:10,030
[Jingcai College Scholarship List Announcement]

128
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:13,750
Mingxi,

129
00:08:13,750 --> 00:08:14,480
you're on it!

130
00:08:17,990 --> 00:08:19,920
Hard work does pay off!

131
00:08:19,950 --> 00:08:22,430
It wasn't easy.

132
00:08:26,470 --> 00:08:27,200
Come with me.

133
00:08:27,430 --> 00:08:27,920
What?

134
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,850
This place is so beautiful!

135
00:08:38,390 --> 00:08:39,250
Not bad, right?

136
00:08:41,669 --> 00:08:43,720
Why didn't you show me this place earlier?

137
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:45,000
So stingy!

138
00:08:47,510 --> 00:08:49,510
I've finally got the scholarship!

139
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:51,600
I can pay my rent

140
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:53,270
and buy shoes now!

141
00:09:01,270 --> 00:09:02,000
Jiang Bohan,

142
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:03,320
thank you.

143
00:09:05,390 --> 00:09:07,250
Why are you suddenly thanking me?

144
00:09:07,910 --> 00:09:10,240
I've been meaning to thank you for a while.

145
00:09:10,670 --> 00:09:12,080
If it weren't for you

146
00:09:12,550 --> 00:09:13,750
and your test papers,

147
00:09:13,910 --> 00:09:16,040
I wouldn't have done so well this time.

148
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,650
Then I'll gladly accept

149
00:09:18,030 --> 00:09:19,000
your thanks.

150
00:09:20,440 --> 00:09:21,120
And

151
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:22,630
I also came back to class

152
00:09:22,630 --> 00:09:23,890
because of you, right?

153
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:25,750
I owe you so much.

154
00:09:26,390 --> 00:09:27,320
Well...

155
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:29,380
just owe me for now.

156
00:09:29,790 --> 00:09:30,990
No rush to pay me back.

157
00:09:32,390 --> 00:09:32,870
But

158
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:34,520
I do charge interest.

159
00:09:35,510 --> 00:09:37,970
As long as you don't charge loan shark rates.

160
00:09:52,510 --> 00:09:53,770
Look, a shooting star!

161
00:09:57,470 --> 00:09:58,600
That's an airplane.

162
00:09:59,100 --> 00:09:59,630
No,

163
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:00,960
there really is one! Come here!

164
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:01,720
Look, look!

165
00:10:02,190 --> 00:10:03,590
It's right there, there!

166
00:10:08,010 --> 00:10:09,140
Isn't it beautiful?

167
00:10:10,270 --> 00:10:11,270
It seems...

168
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,270
it really is.

169
00:10:17,890 --> 00:10:19,810
♪ You are Newton ♪

170
00:10:19,840 --> 00:10:21,570
♪ And I am the apple ♪

171
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:25,000
♪ Falling from the tree ♪

172
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:27,670
So now, do we...

173
00:10:26,280 --> 00:10:27,690
♪ Take a bite ♪

174
00:10:28,180 --> 00:10:32,440
♪ Just like a fish that can't live without water ♪

175
00:10:29,410 --> 00:10:31,940
still need to keep our distance like friends?

176
00:10:32,780 --> 00:10:34,460
♪ You are summer ♪

177
00:10:34,490 --> 00:10:36,450
♪ And I am the breeze ♪

178
00:10:36,270 --> 00:10:36,960
Another shooting star!

179
00:10:36,470 --> 00:10:41,300
♪ Blowing in from the sea ♪

180
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:39,960
Another what?

181
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:41,400
Yu Mingxi, stop trying to change the subject.

182
00:10:41,400 --> 00:10:42,690
♪ I don't understand ♪

183
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:42,640
Did you see it?

184
00:10:42,870 --> 00:10:43,270
No.

185
00:10:43,220 --> 00:10:45,960
♪ Why love always leaves us not knowing ♪

186
00:10:46,410 --> 00:10:47,720
♪ What to do ♪

187
00:11:01,790 --> 00:11:03,590
There's another shooting star.

188
00:11:06,680 --> 00:11:08,360
♪ You are summer ♪

189
00:11:08,380 --> 00:11:10,340
♪ And I am the breeze ♪

190
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:15,190
♪ Blowing in from the sea ♪

191
00:11:15,220 --> 00:11:16,510
♪ Only then do I understand ♪

192
00:11:17,040 --> 00:11:19,780
♪ Why love always leaves us not knowing ♪

193
00:11:20,490 --> 00:11:21,790
♪ What to do ♪

194
00:11:45,550 --> 00:11:46,360
Yu Mingxi,

195
00:11:46,860 --> 00:11:48,790
how could you ever compete with me?

196
00:12:12,130 --> 00:12:12,940
Mingxi,

197
00:12:13,380 --> 00:12:15,790
wasn't Jiang Bohan with you this afternoon?

198
00:12:15,790 --> 00:12:18,250
Why did he go on a date with Qin Siyao tonight?

199
00:12:18,390 --> 00:12:20,250
Look at the screenshot I sent you.

200
00:12:38,270 --> 00:12:39,960
Guys, who can relate?

201
00:12:41,670 --> 00:12:43,520
I'm literally speechless.

202
00:12:44,680 --> 00:12:45,890
Such a turnoff guy.

203
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:09,330
I think we should stop being friends.

204
00:13:09,330 --> 00:13:09,960
Why?

205
00:13:09,980 --> 00:13:11,720
Didn't we just agree yesterday?

206
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:12,840
Because I like you!

207
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:26,000
You casually take those kinds of photos
with another girl,

208
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:27,440
and yet you say you like me?

209
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:28,620
Jiang Bohan.

210
00:13:43,030 --> 00:13:44,630
Why did you get up late today?

211
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:47,090
I didn't sleep well last night.

212
00:13:48,210 --> 00:13:49,070
I'll pick you up

213
00:13:49,080 --> 00:13:50,410
after school today too?

214
00:13:54,460 --> 00:13:55,260
What's wrong?

215
00:13:55,270 --> 00:13:56,070
You seem down.

216
00:13:59,030 --> 00:13:59,560
Nothing.

217
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:03,360
Do boys

218
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:04,960
only hug girls they like?

219
00:14:08,030 --> 00:14:09,690
Wait, Jiang Bohan hugged you?

220
00:14:23,630 --> 00:14:24,290
We're here.

221
00:14:40,550 --> 00:14:41,920
Why is he dropping you off again?

222
00:14:41,920 --> 00:14:42,840
Who takes me to school

223
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:44,240
is none of your business.

224
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:46,000
And what are we, exactly?

225
00:14:46,150 --> 00:14:47,360
Classmates or friends?

226
00:14:47,360 --> 00:14:49,150
Or childhood sweethearts like you and Qin Siyao?

227
00:14:49,150 --> 00:14:50,550
What did she do this time?

228
00:14:52,580 --> 00:14:54,240
I don't want to argue with you.

229
00:14:54,270 --> 00:14:54,800
Corn.

230
00:14:55,720 --> 00:14:57,380
I'll pick you up after school.

231
00:15:10,870 --> 00:15:12,000
Am I crazy?

232
00:15:12,240 --> 00:15:14,510
I actually brought up Qin Siyao in front of him.

233
00:15:14,510 --> 00:15:15,600
Mingxi,

234
00:15:16,390 --> 00:15:18,720
have you fallen for Jiang Bohan?

235
00:15:19,720 --> 00:15:21,150
Whether I like him or not,

236
00:15:21,320 --> 00:15:22,360
what's the point?

237
00:15:23,160 --> 00:15:24,890
Given my current situation...

238
00:15:29,900 --> 00:15:30,570
Yu Mingxi!

239
00:15:32,270 --> 00:15:33,200
Wait for me after school.

240
00:15:33,200 --> 00:15:34,260
I'll take you home.

241
00:15:35,040 --> 00:15:36,300
Thank you, but no need.

242
00:15:47,600 --> 00:15:48,100
Alright,

243
00:15:48,100 --> 00:15:49,840
everyone, go home and review well.

244
00:15:49,840 --> 00:15:50,840
Class dismissed.

245
00:15:55,560 --> 00:15:56,960
What should we eat later?

246
00:15:57,270 --> 00:15:57,670
I don't know.

247
00:15:57,670 --> 00:15:58,720
Do you want to eat at the cafeteria

248
00:15:58,720 --> 00:15:59,550
or dine outside?

249
00:15:59,550 --> 00:16:00,630
I want to dine outside.

250
00:16:00,630 --> 00:16:01,870
I don't want to go to the cafeteria.

251
00:16:01,870 --> 00:16:03,870
What do you want to eat, then?

252
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:06,930
Didn't a new Western restaurant
just open up nearby?

253
00:16:07,290 --> 00:16:08,150
I want to try it.

254
00:16:08,700 --> 00:16:09,770
Do you want that?

255
00:16:09,790 --> 00:16:10,520
Let's go, go.

256
00:16:13,510 --> 00:16:15,170
Why are you avoiding me again?

257
00:16:16,960 --> 00:16:17,820
School is over.

258
00:16:18,870 --> 00:16:20,200
Let's go home together.

259
00:16:21,790 --> 00:16:22,250
No need.

260
00:16:22,720 --> 00:16:23,250
Let's go.

261
00:16:26,800 --> 00:16:27,530
Yu Mingxi.

262
00:16:28,750 --> 00:16:30,150
Stay behind for a moment.

263
00:16:30,710 --> 00:16:31,840
You two go out first.

264
00:16:33,910 --> 00:16:35,510
I'll wait for you at the door.

265
00:16:44,700 --> 00:16:47,120
I heard that you never attend swimming class.

266
00:16:47,120 --> 00:16:48,720
Is it because of your father?

267
00:16:51,510 --> 00:16:52,240
I...

268
00:16:54,900 --> 00:16:57,280
No matter the reason, skipping class isn't right.

269
00:16:57,280 --> 00:17:00,010
The coach was right to make you clean
the natatorium as punishment.

270
00:17:00,010 --> 00:17:01,140
But I want to ask you,

271
00:17:01,350 --> 00:17:03,240
do you plan to just give up that credit?

272
00:17:03,240 --> 00:17:04,099
Headmistress,

273
00:17:04,160 --> 00:17:06,560
may I make up the credit with other classes?

274
00:17:06,589 --> 00:17:07,750
Basketball, track,

275
00:17:08,030 --> 00:17:08,720
running drills,

276
00:17:08,720 --> 00:17:09,869
or even cheerleading.

277
00:17:09,869 --> 00:17:12,660
Jingcai College is a school known for
its swimming program.

278
00:17:12,660 --> 00:17:15,390
Your father, as a coach, was always proud of that.

279
00:17:15,750 --> 00:17:18,410
Every student at Jingcai must learn how to swim.

280
00:17:18,619 --> 00:17:20,250
It's also a survival skill.

281
00:17:22,030 --> 00:17:23,510
But he drowned...

282
00:17:25,109 --> 00:17:26,200
If he were still here,

283
00:17:26,200 --> 00:17:27,130
what do you think

284
00:17:27,640 --> 00:17:28,900
he would want you to do?

285
00:17:36,120 --> 00:17:38,450
Here's the access card to the natatorium.

286
00:17:39,090 --> 00:17:40,750
Remember to find a good coach.

287
00:17:40,790 --> 00:17:41,510
Be safe.

288
00:17:43,790 --> 00:17:45,250
Thank you, Headmistress.

289
00:17:49,070 --> 00:17:51,000
Don't let others know about this.

290
00:17:52,270 --> 00:17:52,720
